p: As shown in Fig. 2C, compared with V-24 h group, cell viability in control, V-1 s, V-10 mins, V-20 mins, V-30 mins, V-40 mins, and V-50 mins groups were significantly increased. There were no significant differences betweenV-60 mins and the V-24 h group, indicating that virions could fully penetrate into host cells within 60 mins of rewarming at 37 °C.
